Title Case Spec

1. Make one letter uppercase - b - B

2. Make one word title uppercase - beowulf - Beowulf

3. Make multiple word title uppercase - beowulf begins - Beowulf Begins

4. Do not capitalize designated words (like prepositions, conjunctions, etc) -
    beowulf from brighton beach - Beowulf from Brighton Beach

5. It capitalizes designated words if they are the first word
                                - from beowulf to the hulk - From Beowulf to the Hulk

6. Ignore non-letter characters - beowulf's revenge - Beowulf's Revenge
                                - 57 beowulfs' - 57 Beowulfs
